## Completed Work This Session

### Project: parley — All 5 phases (Tasks #844-848)
TypeScript drop-in replacement for enquirer (~12M weekly npm downloads). Zero runtime dependencies, Node.js 18+, ESM+CJS dual build.

Core: Base Prompt class with state machine (initial→running→submitted/cancelled), readline raw mode, keypress events, validation, format/result hooks. ANSI escape code utils (cursor, erase, styling, strip). Cross-platform keypress parser (CSI, SS3, alt, ctrl, unicode). Differential terminal renderer.

15 prompt types: Input, Password, Confirm, Select, MultiSelect, Toggle, Number, Autocomplete, Scale, Sort, Snippet, List, Form, Editable, Quiz. All with arrow nav, scroll, disabled choices, wrap-around where applicable.

Enquirer compat layer (`parley/compat/enquirer`): Enquirer class with .prompt() instance+static methods, .register()/.use() plugin system, individual prompt class re-exports.

133 tests across 11 test files. Startup benchmark suite. Strict TypeScript. 5 commits pushed to agentine/parley. CI green. MIT license.

